title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update VII Australia - Photogrammetry Sydney
description:
It has been released: World Update VII Australia. In this video we will do our first flight above Sydney just after the update has been released. Comparing it with before the world update I already see a lot of enhancement so I am pretty enthusiastic. I am not living in Sydney so I can't tell you if it is realistic. If you are living there feel free to leave a comment in the comment box to let us know how realistic it is.
